{"tid":1380889,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"綾瀨遙拍新片遭中国團隊騷擾","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:54:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2db42738a7f236d6aab6bdf99f5b041d7e5f268d","tid":1380889,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"34歲日本女星綾瀨遙，前年偕男星西島秀俊合演劇集《太太，請小心輕放》收視叫好。電影版於上月低調開鏡，但拍攝期間卻發生風波，女主角綾瀨遙疑遭在同幢攝影廠拍攝的中國攝製團隊無禮騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n據知該位於東京的攝影廠內，有不少其他作品同時在內拍攝。有一隊來自內地的攝製團隊，被爆做出無禮行為，除被目擊在攝影廠的禁煙範圍吸煙，又大聲談話影響其他拍攝，碰到綾瀨遙出現時更失晒拿出手機偷拍，又強行圍住她講中文搭訕。<br />\n<br />\n其身邊工作人員對此十分頭痛，擔心會對綾瀨遙帶來危險。故每次出入都安排數名工作人員陪同綾瀨遙，又取消不再到攝影廠飯堂食飯，改為叫外賣到後台休息室進食，以避開該批中國人攝影組。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190729/photo/bkn-20190729132714374-0729_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190729140314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190729%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190729132714374-0729_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190729140314&h=304031b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190729/bkn-20190729132714374-0729_00862_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"65b48b48a08bf459bd242e42d38e4f4395e898ae","tid":1380889,"uid":199893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:36:07.000Z","msg":"不嬲都柒出國際"},{"pid":"1d55ba78f27f1aa38d79497cd7a97581290bd5c1","tid":1380889,"uid":76098,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"小日本妹子有幸被我國青睞還在說三道四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e363b206dcea583acf76dfe89b0c3d4ee741838","tid":1380889,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ab538adeeab04eb77d2a4131e1cbe3cb9be9fe","tid":1380889,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:27:1